link: Vaclav Kotesovec, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
maple: h := proc (i) options operator, arrow; i^3 end proc: g := product((1-x^h(i))/(1-x^i), i = 1 .. 150): gser := series(g, x = 0, 65): seq(coeff(gser, x, n), n = 0 .. 60);
